<item>
            <title>[LU-11101] project inherit should only be changed by root</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11101</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; Currently inherit attribute could be changed by FS_IOC_FSSETXATTR&lt;br/&gt;
 and FS_IOC_SETFLAGS, we have permission check for FS_IOC_FSSETXATTR&lt;br/&gt;
 ,but FS_IOC_SETFLAGS could be done with regular users.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regular users could use this to clear directory inherit attribute which could break directory quota.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
